title: SPY 2013/14 SNOW PK - T3
description:
The T3 combines progressive design, technology, and durability in one heaping helping of a goggle. Take a walk on the wild side without breaking your wallet in the process. 

The T3 is custom built from a flexible polyurethane frame and features patented Scoop® ventilation system, anti-fog cylindrical dual-lens system with anti-scratch protection, a free bonus lens, ergonomic Isotron™ face foam with moisture-wicking Dri-Force™ fleece, silicone-ribbed strap, 100% UV protection, and is helmet compatible with the most popular helmets on the planet.
